Enum KeyLetterEnum

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<KeyLetterEnum>
      • Elements.KeyLetterEnum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<KeyLetterEnum>

    public enum KeyLetterEnum
extends java.lang.Enum<KeyLetterEnum>
    The KeyLetterEnum is used to describe key positions within a scale for a pitch, and is used in conjunction with the KeyPositionEnum to describe a pitch position.
